<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5212113>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Rhagovelia mangle sp. nov. (A) Thorax; arrow shows excavated area of posterior margin of pronotum; dorsal view; male. (B) Part of fore leg; arrow shows grasping comb; male. (C) Part of hind leg; arrow shows tibial spines; male. (D) Proctiger; dorsal view; male. (E) Paramere; lateral view; male. (F) Thorax; arrow shows excavated area of posterior margin of pronotum; dorsal view; female. (G) Part of hind leg; female. (H) Male standing on dorsum of female. Scale bar 1.00 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5212113/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

